I came into this year with many goals. One of them being to write, act and direct my own short film. Six months and 60 pages later, I did just that. Words can’t express how grateful I am to every single person that helped make this happen. I would like to give huge thank you to @justin_the_dp and @thebeaconstudios for believing in this project enough to make it as great as I know it will be. Also, a huge thank you to @bakersfieldcollege for allowing us to film on their campus all week, @big_joes_tacos & @tonyspizzacompany for providing lunches on set, as well as all my friends involved in the cast and crew to bring this project to life. Without you all, none of this would be possible!

Quick recap of all 5 days last week shooting my film.
